title: [PlaybackService] prepare stream asynchonously.
message:
[PlaybackService] prepare stream asynchonously.

Playback service had its own thread but during a synchronous
preparation, no other command could be handled.

Now, stream are prepared off the playback service thread so that
actions such as next/previous/pause can be handled.

title: [Playback] fix audio focus handling.
message:
[Playback] fix audio focus handling.

When the audios focus was gained back, player restarted
even if it was paused from a user action.

Now, playback restart on audio focus gain only if the
player was paused due to audio focus loss.
